code: @Override public boolean equals(Object other) {     if (this == other) {         return true.     }     if (other == null) {         return false.     }     if (this.getClass() != other.getClass()) {         return false.     }     PurchaseOrder that = (PurchaseOrder) other.     return this.product.equals(that.product) && this.amount == that.amount. }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return product.hashCode() * 37 + (int) Math.round(amount). }
@Override public String toString() {     return "PurchaseOrder[" + product + " x " + amount + "]". }
